# Doodle Jump Game

A browser-based recreation of the classic Doodle Jump game built with vanilla JavaScript and HTML5 Canvas.

## ğŸ“‹ Description

This is a simple implementation of the popular Doodle Jump mobile game where players control a character that jumps automatically and must land on platforms to climb higher while avoiding falling off the screen.

## ğŸ® How to Play

- **Move Left:** Press `A` or `â†` (Left Arrow)
- **Move Right:** Press `D` or `â†’` (Right Arrow)
- **Restart:** Press `Space` when game is over

### Objective
- Keep the doodler jumping on platforms
- Climb as high as possible to increase your score
- Avoid falling off the bottom of the screen

## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- A modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
- The following image assets in an `Assets` folder:
  - `doodlejumpbg.png` - Background image
  - `doodler-right.png` - Character facing right
  - `doodler-left.png` - Character facing left
  - `platform.png` - Platform image

